# UI Launch Breakage Prevention Rule

Reference: `konnakol_trainer/docs/agent-playbooks/ui-launch-breakage-prevention.md`.

Apply this rule whenever agent changes include at least one of:
- export/import edits in TS/JS modules,
- revert/restore of recently edited logic files,
- cross-file refactor affecting symbol ownership.

Mandatory actions before claiming "UI fixed":
- Run `npm run build` in `konnakol_trainer` first.
- If build shows unresolved export/import, fix symbol contract immediately (producer or consumer).
- Start `npm run dev` only after successful build.
- Treat white screen as probable module/runtime failure before investigating ports/network.
